Package javax.security.identitystore.persistence.cachedsource

The Identity Store Persistence Cached Source API package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CachedIdentityStoreSource
    CachedIdentityStoreSource provides common behavior for CachedIdentityStore identity data source implementations.
    CachedIdentityStoreSource.CallerSource
    CallerSource is an in-memory representation of the caller data stored in a source.
    CachedIdentityStoreSource.CredentialSource
    CredentialSource is an in-memory representation of the credential data stored in a source.
    JsonFileIdentityStoreSource
    JsonFileIdentityStoreSource is a CachedIdentityStoreSource implementation which determines identity data from a given JSON file.
    MemoryIdentityStoreSource
    MemoryIdentityStoreSource is a CachedIdentityStoreSource implementation which determines identity data from a given collection.

Package javax.security.identitystore.persistence.cachedsource Description

The Identity Store Persistence Cached Source API package. This package contains classes implementing CachedIdentityStoreSource, which supplies data for the CachedIdentityStore. Each source is associated with a persistence mechanism, such as a file, which would be read in its entirety and cached in the CachedIdentityStoreSource.
Version:
1.0
